<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَشَاءُ أَنْ يَكْشِفَ عَنْهُمْ عِنْدَ نُزُولِ الْعَذَابِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{وَتَنْسَوْنَ مَا تُشْرِكُونَ}</span> بِاللَّهِ مِنْ هَذِهِ الْأَوْثَانِ؛ فَتُعْرِضُونَ عَنْهَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سُورَة الْأَنْعَام من الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> إِلَى الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>